.TH "LIGHTNING-ROUTE-FIND" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-route-find \- find a payment route to a Lightning node
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning route-find
.I pubkey sat
.RB [ --riskfactor
.IR N ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Finds a payment route to
.I pubkey
for
.I sat
satoshis using
.BR lightning-cli (1)
.BR getroute .
Returns JSON:
.nf
{
  "hops": [{"id":"...","channel":"...","direction":<int>,
            "amount_msat":<int>,"delay":<int>}, ...],
  "total_msat": <int>,
  "fee_msat":   <int>
}
.fi
.TP
.B --riskfactor N
Risk factor for the pathfinding algorithm (default 1).
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Route found.
.TP
.B 5
No route to destination.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-peer-connect (1),
.BR lightning-channel-open (1)
